This is a simple extension to bulk delete Gemini conversations by the addition of checkboxes.

It's very simple. You can afford deletion of gemini conversations with just a few clicks and within seconds.

However there is a known issue which at the moment leads to hovering first on any conversation to make Extension available to handle the deletion, cause of some development limits due to Gemini Source page hiding some needed stuff.

Watch out the extension GitHub Repository. Contribution is really appreciated!

Credits: 
ChatGPT Bulk Delete Extension for an overall quick look for how to handle deletion properly and setup extension, also cause idea was taken from it to perform the same thing on Gemini.
